      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a project or a parts car. The engine currently runs roughly and will require significant mechanical attention, and the transmission shifts harshly. Externally, the body shows noticeable rust, several dents, and fading paint, while the interior has significant tearing in the upholstery and non-functional electronics. Please expect to invest time and resources into repairs to make this vehicle roadworthy again.",
